des:
PAJ GPS FINDER Skill helps you to locate your devices in an easy way, just with your voice, asking for example:
Where is my device? o What is the last location of my device?
You only need to authenticate with your PAJ GPS account data and you can use this skill.
To share your feedback you can contact us at info@paj-gps.de
